---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>Long-Span Suspension Bridge | Mateng Cheng</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Long-span suspension bridge 3D CAD modeling and structural analysis project by Mateng Cheng."
		/>
	</head>

	<body>
		<header class="site-header">
			<nav>
				<a href="/" class="logo">Mateng Cheng</a>

				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="/">Home</a>
					<a href="/#projects">Projects</a>
					<a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
				</div>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<main>
			<section class="project-hero">
				<a class="back-link" href="/#projects">← Back to Projects</a>

				<p class="eyebrow">Structural Analysis · 3D CAD Modeling</p>

				<h1>Long-Span Suspension Bridge 3D CAD Modeling & Structural Analysis</h1>

				<p class="hero-text">
					An engineering modeling and analysis project focused on developing an integrated
					3D bridge model, generating technical visualizations, and performing structural
					response analysis for a long-span cable-supported bridge system.
				</p>

				<div class="project-meta">
					<div>
						<span>Tools</span>
						<p>SAP2000, AutoCAD 3D</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<span>Project Type</span>
						<p>Structural Modeling & Analysis</p>
					</div>

					<div>
						<span>Institution</span>
						<p>Columbia University</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="section">
				<img
					class="hero-image"
					src="/projects/suspension-bridge/bridge-overview.jpg"
					alt="3D rendering of the long-span suspension bridge"
				/>
			</section>

			<section class="section two-column">
				<div>
					<h2>Project Overview</h2>
				</div>

				<div>
					<p>
						This project involved the development of an integrated 3D structural model and
						topographic model for an 800 m main-span suspension bridge. The work connected
						bridge geometry, terrain context, visual representation, and structural analysis
						to support design communication and technical review.
					</p>

					<p>
						The project also included structural response studies using SAP2000 under several
						modeling scenarios, including dead load, prestress loss, and cable failure cases.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="section two-column">
				<div>
					<h2>My Role</h2>
				</div>

				<div>
					<ul class="role-list">
						<li>Built the 3D bridge and terrain model for design visualization.</li>
						<li>Generated plan, section, and detail views from the 3D model.</li>
						<li>Performed SAP2000 vibration and structural response analyses.</li>
						<li>Summarized analysis results and supported iterative model refinement.</li>
						<li>Maintained consistent model layers, annotations, and geometric coordination.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="section">
				<div class="section-title">
					<h2>Project Gallery</h2>
					<p>3D bridge model, roadway perspective, CAD model view, and SAP2000 analysis output.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="gallery-grid">
					<figure>
						<img
							src="/projects/suspension-bridge/bridge-overview.jpg"
							alt="Overall 3D rendering of the bridge"
						/>
						<figcaption>Overall 3D bridge model and surrounding terrain context.</figcaption>
					</figure>

					<figure>
						<img
							src="/projects/suspension-bridge/bridge-roadway-view.jpg"
							alt="Roadway perspective of the bridge model"
						/>
						<figcaption>Roadway-level view showing tower, deck, and cable layout.</figcaption>
					</figure>

					<figure>
						<img
							src="/projects/suspension-bridge/bridge-cad-model.png"
							alt="CAD view of bridge cable and terrain model"
						/>
						<figcaption>CAD-based bridge model showing cable geometry and site context.</figcaption>
					</figure>

					<figure>
						<img
							src="/projects/suspension-bridge/bridge-sap2000-analysis.png"
							alt="SAP2000 structural analysis result"
						/>
						<figcaption>SAP2000 structural response visualization under analysis scenario.</figcaption>
					</figure>
				</div>
			</section>

			
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:global(*) {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	:global(html) {
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	:global(body) {
		margin: 0;
		font-family:
			Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
			sans-serif;
		color: #1f2933;
		background: #f7f4ef;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	a {
		color: inherit;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.site-header {
		position: sticky;
		top: 0;
		z-index: 10;
		background: rgba(247, 244, 239, 0.92);
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e5dfd3;
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	nav {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1360px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.logo {
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		color: #111827;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.nav-links {
		margin-left: auto;
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #4b5563;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: flex-end;
	}

	.nav-links a {
		padding: 0.45rem 0.85rem;
		border: 1px solid #c9bba6;
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-weight: 700;
		background: #fffaf2;
		color: #8a5a28;
		white-space: nowrap;
		transition:
			background 0.15s ease,
			color 0.15s ease,
			border-color 0.15s ease,
			transform 0.15s ease;
	}

	.nav-links a:hover {
		background: #1f2933;
		border-color: #1f2933;
		color: #ffffff;
		transform: translateY(-1px);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 1120px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem;
	}

	.project-hero {
		padding: 5.5rem 0 3.5rem;
		max-width: 960px;
	}

	.back-link {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: #8a5a28;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.back-link:hover {
		color: #111827;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.16em;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #8a5a28;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 1050px;
		font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.2vw, 3.7rem);
		line-height: 1.08;
		letter-spacing: -0.04em;
		color: #111827;
	}

	.hero-text {
		max-width: 820px;
		margin: 1.4rem 0 0;
		font-size: 1.18rem;
		color: #4b5563;
	}

	.project-meta {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.project-meta div {
		background: #fffaf2;
		border: 1px solid #e5dfd3;
		border-radius: 18px;
		padding: 1rem;
	}

	.project-meta span {
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		color: #8a5a28;
	}

	.project-meta p {
		margin: 0;
		color: #111827;
		font-size: 1.08rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.section {
		padding: 3.5rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid #e5dfd3;
	}

	.hero-image {
		width: 100%;
		max-height: 520px;
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 24px;
		border: 1px solid #e5dfd3;
		box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(31, 41, 51, 0.09);
	}

	.two-column {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 0.45fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 2rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		color: #111827;
	}

	p {
		color: #4b5563;
	}

	.two-column p:first-child {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	.role-list {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.15rem;
		color: #4b5563;
	}

	.role-list li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.section-title h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}

	.section-title p {
		margin: 0;
		color: #6b7280;
	}

	.gallery-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	figure {
		margin: 0;
		background: #fffaf2;
		border: 1px solid #e5dfd3;
		border-radius: 22px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(31, 41, 51, 0.06);
	}

	figure img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: 280px;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	figcaption {
		padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
		color: #4b5563;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		nav {
			align-items: flex-start;
			gap: 0.9rem;
			flex-direction: column;
			padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		}

		.nav-links {
			display: flex;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			justify-content: flex-start;
			gap: 0.55rem;
			width: 100%;
		}

		.nav-links a {
			padding: 0.38rem 0.65rem;
			font-size: 0.82rem;
			line-height: 1.1;
		}

		.project-hero {
			padding: 4.5rem 0 3rem;
		}

		.project-meta,
		.two-column,
		.gallery-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		figure img {
			height: 220px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 420px) {
		.nav-links {
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.nav-links a {
			padding: 0.35rem 0.58rem;
			font-size: 0.78rem;
		}

		.logo {
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}
	}
</style>